snippet.title: Into The Unknown - Official Trailer #1
snippet.description:
This is the official trailer for the indie game "Into The Unknown" By FYRE Games.  Be sure to check it out on Itch.io, Gamejollt, and Steam!

Itch.io: https://fyre-games.itch.io/into-the-unknown
Gamejolt: http://gamejolt.com/games/into-the-unknown/176057
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/553130?beta=1

Thanks for playing!
